                <aside class="toc-container">
                    <h3>On this page</h3>
                    <div class="toc">
                        <div class="toc">
<ul>
<li><a href="#a-divers-journal-the-gilded-grimoire">A Diver's Journal: The Gilded Grimoire</a><ul>
<li><a href="#recovered-from-the-ossified-remains-of-scribe-xanthus-concord-lyceum-508-ae-dissemination-forbidden">Recovered from the ossified remains of Scribe Xanthus, Concord Lyceum, 508 AE. Dissemination forbidden.</a></li>
